---

<section
    class="section-exploration relative py-32 md:py-48 px-6 md:px-12 overflow-visible bg-transparent"
>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-[-1] bg-[#121212]"></div>

        <div
            class="absolute top-[10%] left-[-10%] w-[70%] h-[80%] bg-[#1D2F40]/40 blur-[160px] rounded-full mix-blend-screen opacity-70"
        >
        </div>

        <div
            class="absolute bottom-[10%] right-[-10%] w-[60%] h-[80%] bg-[#F24405]/20 blur-[150px] rounded-full mix-blend-screen opacity-60"
        >
        </div>

        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#1D2F40]/20 via-transparent to-[#F24405]/10 opacity-95"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-[1700px] mx-auto relative z-20 flex flex-col gap-24">
        <div
            class="w-full text-center space-y-8 translate-x-[0px] translate-y-[0px]"
        >
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
                <span
                    class="text-[#F2E394] text-[10px] font-cinzel font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.5em]"
                    >Un Mundo en Expansión</span
                >
                <div
                    class="h-[1px] w-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#A6483F] to-transparent"
                >
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2
                class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-cinzel font-bold leading-none text-[#F2E394] tracking-tighter"
            >
                Horas de <br />
                <span
                    class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#F2E394] via-[#F24405] to-[#A6483F]"
                >
                    Aventura Pura
                </span>
            </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-20">
            <div
                class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-32 items-center"
            >
                <div class="relative group translate-x-[0px] translate-y-[0px]">
                    <div
                        class="absolute -inset-10 bg-[#1D2F40]/5 blur-[80px] rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative w-full p-1 border border-[#1D2F40]/30 bg-[#0D0D0D] shadow-2xl"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-12 h-12 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-[#1D2F40] z-30 m-[-2px] opacity-40"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-video">
                            <img
                                src="/GreedFall/Olima_Landscape.jpg"
                                alt="Escenarios de decisión"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-[3000ms] group-hover:scale-105 opacity-80"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left gap-6 translate-x-[0px] translate-y-[0px]"
                >
                    <p
                        class="font-serif italic text-2xl md:text-4xl text-[#F2E394] leading-tight border-l-4 border-[#1D2F40] pl-8 py-2"
                    >
                        Más de 40 horas de juego, con distintos escenarios en
                        función de tus decisiones.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-32 items-center"
            >
                <div
                    class="order-2 md:order-1 flex flex-col items-center md:items-end text-center md:text-right gap-6 translate-x-[0px] translate-y-[0px]"
                >
                    <p
                        class="font-serif italic text-2xl md:text-4xl text-[#F2E394] leading-tight border-r-4 border-[#F24405] pr-8 py-2"
                    >
                        Explora majestuosos países y opulentas ciudades
                        inspiradas en la Europa del siglo XVII.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="order-1 md:order-2 relative group translate-x-[0px] translate-y-[0px]"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute -inset-10 bg-[#1D2F40]/20 blur-[80px] rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative w-full p-1 border border-[#F2E394]/20 bg-[#0D0D0D] shadow-2xl"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-12 h-12 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-[#F2E394] z-30 m-[-2px] opacity-40"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-video">
                            <img
                                src="/GreedFall/GreedFall_TheDyingWorld_Screenshot05.png"
                                alt="Ciudades opulentas"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-[3000ms] group-hover:scale-105 opacity-80"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .section-exploration {
        contain: paint;
        mask-image: linear-gradient(
            to bottom,
            transparent,
            black 10%,
            black 90%,
            transparent
        );
    }
</style>
